Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
for freshman it is a good thing.

first, most of these freshman are the first time to live away from home. living on campus can help them adjust to the life quickly.

second. they are more constrained than living off campus. so they can focus more on studies.

last. they can be more social and make friends with others.